    </div>
    
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/minecraft">Minecraft</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terraria">Terraria</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about" class="active">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <header>
        <h1>About Nieuserver.online</h1>
        <p>Learn about our mission, team, and what makes our servers special</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2024, Nieuserver.online began as a passion project between friends who wanted to create high-quality gaming experiences. What started as a small Minecraft server has grown into a multi-game community hub launching in 2025.</p>
            <p>We believe in player-driven worlds where creativity and community thrive. Our servers are designed to be welcoming spaces for both casual and dedicated gamers.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Server Features</h2>
            <p><strong>What sets us apart:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #b0b0b0;">
                <li>99.9% uptime guaranteed</li>
                <li>Dedicated hardware for lag-free gameplay</li>
                <li>Regular content updates and events</li>
                <li>Balanced modpacks (optional for Minecraft)</li>
                <li>Active admin team against griefing</li>
                <li>Cross-platform support where possible</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our Terraria server will feature custom biomes and challenges, while our Minecraft server offers both vanilla and modded experiences.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <h2 style="text-align: center; color: #4CAF50; margin: 40px 0 20px;">Meet the Team</h2>
        
        <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Founder">
                <h3>Alex Nieuwenhuis</h3>
                <div class="role">Founder & Server Architect</div>
                <p>10+ years of server administration experience. Builds the tech that makes our worlds run smoothly.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/44.jpg" alt="Community Manager">
                <h3>Jamie Rivera</h3>
                <div class="role">Community Manager</div>
                <p>Creates welcoming spaces and organizes epic in-game events. Your go-to for server questions.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="team-member">
                <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/67.jpg" alt="Content Designer">
                <h3>Sam Chen</h3>
                <div class="role">Content Designer</div>
                <p>Designs custom Terraria biomes and Minecraft mod integrations. The creative force behind our worlds.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pixel-divider"></div>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <p><strong>Community First:</strong> We actively listen to player feedback through Discord and in-game polls.</p>
            <p><strong>Fair Play:</strong> Strict anti-cheat measures with transparent moderation policies.</p>
            <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> Regular seasonal events and gameplay twists to keep things fresh.</p>
            <p><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Servers optimized for global players with multiple world regions.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 <span class="domain">nieuserver.online</span></p>
        <p>Crafting memorable gaming experiences since 2024</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>